schools.name: Edna And John W. Mosley P-8

data.description:
Welcome to this 2-story townhome which offers a blend of comfort, convenience, and recreation within the Americana Community. 
The open floor plan with lots of natural light has a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings and wood wood-burning fireplace, connecting to the kitchen, perfect for cozy gatherings or relaxation.
Upstairs is a bedroom with a built-in desk and a full bathroom. The laundry is conveniently located on the main floor and complete with a washer and dryer.
The private patio is accessible from the kitchen, ideal for outdoor enjoyment and hosting guests. 
Residents of this townhome also have access to community amenities such as a pool and tennis courts, offering opportunities for leisure and recreation just steps away from your front door. Plus, the strategic location near major transportation routes like 225 and 6th Avenue makes commuting to key destinations such as the Denver Tech Center and downtown Denver a breeze.
